data.description: Gorgeous completely remodeled ranch home in Warrensburg! You'll love all the little details the owner added including luxury vinyl flooring throughout, updated lighting, new interior paint, shiplap fireplace detailing, finished basement, updated kitchen including subway tile and new dishwasher and microwave! Finished basement features a non-conforming bedroom, bathroom, family room space and the workshop area is perfect for the wood worker or hobbyist! Primary bedroom has closet system and full bathroom. The home has so much space for the family to spread out including a formal family room. Check out the community pool that's open for residents and guests, available for parties. Plus use of the huge lot in the middle. Everything is completed for you and all you have to do is bring your things! You will love it here!!!
